nodes.text: Jaanu was a female witch-like minion of the Sith Lord and Separatist leader Count Dooku who lived during the last years of the Galactic Republic. She wielded twin red-bladed lightsabers and piloted a skiff. Jaanu was defeated by the Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker on the planet Tatooine during the inter-galactic Clone Wars, an conflict which raged between 22 and 19 BBY.
Jaanu was first mentioned in The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia (2008), a book published by Del Rey.
